---
description: Prevent train/test leakage in ML pipeline code
globs: src/**/*.py,scripts/**/*.py
alwaysApply: false
---

# No Data Leakage

- Split train/test BEFORE fitting preprocessors.
- Fit `ColumnTransformer` and models only on training data (inside sklearn `Pipeline` or explicit train slice).
- Hyperparameter tuning: 5-fold CV on train split only; never use test labels for selection.
- Main selection metric: macro F1.
- Sensitive attributes (`sex`, `race`) may be dropped only for EXT-001 extension experiments.
